information: Orienco, founded in 1990 is a wholesaler specializing in importing, processing (grilling, coating, salting), packing and distributing nuts. The nuts are sourced direct from the harvesters all over the world and from specialist top-ranking international importers. This enables us to guarantee not only the good quality of the raw materials but also the continuity of supplies. The nuts are processed in compliance with hygiene and food safety regulations: grilling, salting, coating in different flavours and packing. Treat yourself to our pistachios, almonds, cashew nuts, peanuts, raisins, hazelnuts, walnuts, coconuts, pecans, Macadamia nuts, sesame seeds, pine nuts, pumpkin and sunflower seeds, chick peas and so on. Orienco is the guarantee of working with a high quality wholesaler.
